"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-football-paris-2024-olympics-football-draw-how-to-watch-tv-channel-live-stream-start-time-teams-today-b1146429.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Football  The draw for the 2024Paris Olympicsis about to take place for both the men's and women's tournaments.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil have failed to qualify to defend their men's gold medal while Canada are out to retain the women's crown, afterTeam GBmissed out on a spot due to their early exit from the Nations League.\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9876338859217759, \"rank\": 0.01189859591109233, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8908423589701937, \"rank\": 0.12253298520107629, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 16 teams will be split into four groups for the men's tournament while the women's will divide 12 teams into three groups, meaning the best two third-placed teams will qualify for the knockouts.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As per usual, the men'sOlympicsteams will be predominantly made up of players under the age of 23 with no restrictions on the women's squads.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheOlympic footballdraw takes place tonight, Wednesday March 20, 2024 in the Pulse building which is the headquarters of the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is set to begin a 7pm GMT.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Men's  Pot 1  Pot 2  Pot 3  Pot 4  Three Asian nations, plus a play-off between the fourth-placed team at the U23 Asian Cup and fourth-placed team at the U23 Africa Cup of Nations, Guinea, will decide the final four spots.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"score\": 0.9999999999351985, \"rank\": 6.483885631101286e-11, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\"}, {\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_AFC_Asian_Cup\", \"score\": 0.8116627685903909, \"rank\": 0.23179129517212763, \"text\": \"Asian Cup\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_AFC_Asian_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_AFC_Asian_Cup\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women's  Pot 1  Pot 2  Pot 3  Pot 4  Two African nations will qualify in April's play-offs, which see South Africa face Nigeria and Zambia take on Morocco.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999971897273934, \"rank\": 2.8083585796392162e-06, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7512962985609183, \"rank\": 0.3310327617644538, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999999907821352, \"rank\": 8.635451671495094e-08, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999898093392, \"rank\": 1.018673646737335e-08, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TV channel and live stream:The draw will be broadcast live and for free online via the FIFA+ streaming service.\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 